<div id="review_39027723" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/39027723" />
    <a title="Manny" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/1713956-manny"><img alt="Manny" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1442491692p2/1713956.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/39027723?book_show_action=true">Dec 01, 2008</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Manny" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Manny" href="/user/show/1713956-manny">Manny</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="really liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">really liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>



        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/1713956-manny?shelf=french">french</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/1713956-manny?shelf=strongly-recommended">strongly-recommended</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/1713956-manny?shelf=why-not-call-it-poetry">why-not-call-it-poetry</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer39027723" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer1167453387819696970"><br/>One of the all-time great over-the-top romances - everyone knows the story, and it&apos;s been adapted a million times. How they could have given it a happy ending in Steve Martin&apos;s &quot;Roxanne&quot; is beyond me. The Depardieu movie is the one to see, of course. </span>
  <span id="freeText1167453387819696970" style="display:none"><br />One of the all-time great over-the-top romances - everyone knows the story, and it's been adapted a million times. How they could have given it a happy ending in Steve Martin's "Roxanne" is beyond me. The Depardieu movie is the one to see, of course. </span>
  <a data-text-id="1167453387819696970" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


      <div class="reviewFooter uitext buttons">
          

