          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/18967405-loretta?shelf=classic">classic</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/18967405-loretta?shelf=my-2021-reading-challenge">my-2021-reading-challenge</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/18967405-loretta?shelf=plays">plays</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/18967405-loretta?shelf=january-2021">january-2021</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3721996401" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer7100566718785090995">Enjoyable play with enjoyable characters especially Cyrano who I felt extremely sorry for. Who in life hasn’t “liked” someone who didn’t even know you were alive...?</span>

          </span>
        </div>


