<div id="review_2363735" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/2363735" />
    <a title="Elf" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/129963-elf"><img alt="Elf" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1181768089p2/129963.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/2363735?book_show_action=true">Jun 25, 2007</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Elf" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Elf" href="/user/show/129963-elf">Elf</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="did not like it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">did not like it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Paperback 9780451525482" href="/book/show/424764.Cyrano_de_Bergerac">review of another edition</a>


        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2363735" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer1003309061224662790">I absolutely despise this particular translation. As soon as I get home I&apos;ll look up who did it. But I know this cover. <br/><br/>It&apos;s done in bad prose which does not suit this heart-wrenching play at all. <br/><br/>Stay away from this translation and either pick up a copy in the original french or try Brian Hooker&apos;s translation.</span>
  <span id="freeText1003309061224662790" style="display:none">I absolutely despise this particular translation. As soon as I get home I'll look up who did it. But I know this cover. <br /><br />It's done in bad prose which does not suit this heart-wrenching play at all. <br /><br />Stay away from this translation and either pick up a copy in the original french or try Brian Hooker's translation.</span>
  <a data-text-id="1003309061224662790" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


